{
  "hooks": {
    "SessionStart": [
      {
        "matcher": "startup|resume|clear|compact",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "prompt",
            "prompt": "ztl-coder v3.0.0 loaded.\n\n**Available Primary Agents:**\n- ztl-coder-commander - Main orchestrator for complex tasks\n- ztl-coder-brainstormer - Design exploration and refined requirements\n- ztl-coder-octto - Browser-based interactive brainstorming\n\n**Available Subagents:**\n- planner - Create implementation plans\n- executor - Orchestrate implement→review cycles
- implementer - Execute specific tasks
- reviewer - Code review
- codebase-locator - Find file locations
- codebase-analyzer - Deep module analysis
- pattern-finder - Find existing patterns
- project-initializer - Initialize project docs
- ledger-creator - Create continuity ledgers
- artifact-searcher - Search past work
\n\n**Commands:**\n- /ztl-coder-init - Initialize project with ARCHITECTURE.md and CODE_STYLE.md
- /ztl-coder-ledger - Create/update continuity ledger
- /ztl-coder-search - Search past handoffs, plans, available ledgers
\n\n**MCP Tools:**\n- ztl_code_look_at - View file structure
- ztl_code_artifact_search - Search artifacts
- ztl_code_ast_grep_search - AST-based code search
- ztl_code_ast_grep_replace - AST-based code replacement
- ztl_code_pty_* - PTY session management

**Workflow:** Brainstorm → Plan → Implement → Review
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PreToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Write|Edit",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/scripts/think-mode-trigger.sh"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PostToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Write",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/scripts/artifact-indexer.sh"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
